---

This project includes code ported from:

- Clicky (https://github.com/farzaa/clicky) — MIT License
  * The companion voice system prompt and [POINT:x,y:label:screenN]
    parsing logic
  * The quadratic Bezier flight animation (smoothstep easing,
    tangent-based rotation, sin-pulse scale)

- screen-copilot (https://github.com/Gvascons/screen-copilot) — MIT License
  * The `_NET_WM_STATE_ABOVE` ClientMessage always-on-top helper
  * The `claude -p` subprocess integration pattern
  * The GTK4 + Adwaita floating overlay window chrome

Both projects are licensed under the MIT license.
